<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DeskZone - Coś poszło nie tak</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4f46e5;
            --primary-hover: #4338ca;
            --background: #f8fafc;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #0f172a;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --danger: #ef4444;
        }

        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 50px 20px; 
            background-color: var(--background); 
            color: var(--text-main); 
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 80vh;
        }

        .error-container { 
            background: var(--surface); 
            padding: 40px; 
            border-radius: 16px; 
            display: inline-block; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.03); 
            max-width: 500px; 
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        h1 { 
            color: var(--danger); 
            font-size: 56px; 
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px; 
        }

        h2 { 
            color: var(--text-main); 
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 0; 
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p { 
            color: var(--text-muted); 
            font-size: 1rem; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .btn { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: var(--primary); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 12px 24px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            font-weight: 600; 
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, transform 0.1s; 
        }

        .btn:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); }
        .btn:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>⚠️</h1>
        <h2>Wystąpił błąd aplikacji</h2>
        <p><%= errorMessage %></p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">🏠 Powrót do strony głównej</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>